      <td style="text-align: center">2</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">3</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">3</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">4</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">4</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">5</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">5</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>The Barracks Tower locations are predetermined by the <a href="../../source/buildings/barracks">Barracks</a> that you choose. They are placed in specific locations to fit within the Barracks.</p>

